message.content: cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DB, cs.CYBER, cs.SY - This paper involves the collection and analysis of real-world IoT data, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to identify IoT data sources and a large-scale data collection process. It also involves data management and analysis, which falls under the categories of database (DB) and cyber security (CYBER). Additionally, the paper discusses future challenges and open research problems in the IoT area, which could fall under the categories of social implications (SI) and systems and control (SY).
